msgctxt "an7.39:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.39:0.2"
msgid "4. devatāvagga "
msgstr "4. Deities "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an7.39:0.3"
msgid "39. Dutiyapaṭisambhidāsutta "
msgstr "39. Textual Analysis (2nd) "

# NOTE: See BB’s note for the “historical present” in this text. These texts on the patisambhidas appear to be carelessly hammered together, with Sariputta as the authorizer of the Theravada school, to buttress this obscure set of dhammas, which became a lietmotif of Theravada.
#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an7.39:1.1"
msgid "“Sattahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato sāriputto catasso paṭisambhidā sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, having seven qualities, Sāriputta realized the four kinds of textual analysis and lives having achieved them with his own insight. "

msgctxt "an7.39:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi sattahi? "
msgstr "What seven? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.39:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, sāriputto ‘idaṃ me cetaso līnattan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti; "
msgstr "It’s when Sāriputta truly understood: ‘This is mental sluggishness’. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.39:1.4"
msgid "ajjhattaṃ saṅkhittaṃ vā cittaṃ ‘ajjhattaṃ me saṅkhittaṃ cittan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti; "
msgstr "He truly understood internally constricted mind as ‘internally constricted mind’. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.39:1.5"
msgid "bahiddhā vikkhittaṃ vā cittaṃ ‘bahiddhā me vikkhittaṃ cittan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti; "
msgstr "He truly understood externally scattered mind as ‘externally scattered mind’. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.39:1.6"
msgid "tassa viditā vedanā uppajjanti, viditā upaṭṭhahanti, viditā abbhatthaṃ gacchanti; "
msgstr "He knew feelings, perceptions, and thoughts as they arose, as they remained, and as they went away. "

msgctxt "an7.39:1.7"
msgid "viditā saññā … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.39:1.8"
msgid "vitakkā uppajjanti, viditā upaṭṭhahanti, viditā abbhatthaṃ gacchanti; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.39:1.9"
msgid "sappāyāsappāyesu kho panassa dhammesu hīnappaṇītesu kaṇhasukkasappaṭibhāgesu nimittaṃ suggahitaṃ sumanasikataṃ sūpadhāritaṃ suppaṭividdhaṃ paññāya. "
msgstr "The patterns of qualities—suitable or unsuitable, inferior or superior, or those on the side of dark or bright—were properly grasped, attended, borne in mind, and comprehended with wisdom. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.39:1.10"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, sattahi dhammehi samannāgato sāriputto catasso paṭisambhidā sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharatī”ti. "
msgstr "Having these seven qualities, Sāriputta realized the four kinds of textual analysis and lives having achieved them with his own insight.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.39:1.11"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

